PLANTS OF NORTH CAROLINA
Brunswick Co.

*Galax urceolata* (Poiret) Brummitt

Bryant Mill Ck., a tributary of Cape Fear R.
in extreme N.E. corner of Co. USGS Acme
quadrangle. 20 - 30 % creek slope. Soil sandy
loam, occasional limestone outcrops. Canopy
mixed hardwood, *Q. alba* or *Fagus* dominant.
